HEADWORD: Reckoner
<hw>Reck"on*er</hw> <pr>(r⟦ecr⟧k"'n*⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One who reckons or computes; also, a book of calculations, tables,
etc., to assist in reckoning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Reckoners</qex> without their host must reckon twice.</q>
<rj><qau>Camden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reckoning</ent>⟦br⟧
